query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('autolayout',
'calendar',
'configuration',
'ember.js',
'get',
'google-chrome-extension',
'jasper-reports',
'jvm',
'onclick',
'pagination',
'passwords',
'tomcat',
'windows',
'zend-framework');
